\id 2PE - consultant approved, ready for publication
\h 2 Pita
\toc3 2PI
\toc2 2 Pita
\toc1 Pitan Ak…®nafarir Namba 2
\mt1 Pitan Ak…®nafarir Namba 2
\mt2 O
\mt1 2 Pita
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n akar m…®ngarimra kara. Tisan maba arua Krais…®n adarazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba ko arazir aghuibagh as…®ghas…®si. Ez…® Pita ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven m…®g…®a ghaze, Krais…®n adarazi men akaba baraghan mark…®. Me, akar aposelba men sure gamizibar suiragh gavgafigh. Eght…® arazir kam…®n me God ko Ekiam Krais Iesus derav…®ra aning g…®fogham. Aposelba uari uan damazibar Iesus…®n ganigha uaghan a barazi, a men sure gami.
\ip Gumazir maba kamagh…®n m…®gei Iesus ua izan kogham. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam ghaze, a izam. Guizbang…®ra a zuam…®ra izeghan koghamin bizim…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n: God gumazitam o amizitam ovengan aghua. A kamaghsua, gumazamiziba bar navibagh iragham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gumazamiziba dughiam me gan…®ga, egha me m…®zua ikiav…®ra iti (3:9).
\c 1
\ms1 E arazir aghuibar amut…® da en navir averiabar ik…® gavgavigham, // eght…® e gumazamizir kurabar akaba batogham
\mr (Sapta 1--3)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Korin 4:13; Efesus 4:5; Taitus 1:4\x*K…® Saimon Pita, k…® Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazim ko an aposel. K…®, ia gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir aghuim itiba, akar kam ia bagha an osiri. Krais Iesus en God, a en Akurvazir Gumazim. Egha a uan arazir aghuim…®n God n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir aghuim ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam, a enanam ko vorogh…®ra ghu.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Jut 1:2\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia God ko en Ekiam Iesus, aning…®n fofozir aghuim inis. Ez…® kamagh…®n apangkuvir arazim ko navir am…®rizim ian ekevegh ik…®.
\s1 God ua baghav…®ra e am…®sefe
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Jon 17:3; 2 Tesalonika 2:14; 2 Timoti 1:9; 1 Pita 2:9\x*Krais Iesus a God, an gavgavim a biziba bar e gan…®ngi. Eght…® da gavgavim e dan…®ngt…®ma, e ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim iniva e God ifongezir arazibar amu ikiam. E Krais g…®fo, ez…® fofozir kam e gamima e God ifongezir arazibagh ami. Ez…® a ko itir arazim ko an arazir aghuim…®n, an en dia.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2 Korin 7:1; Efesus 4:24; 2 Pita 2:18-20; 1 Jon 3:2\x*Egha bizir bar aghuiba e gan…®ngi, da bar ekefe. Ez…® kar bizir a fom…®ra e dan…®ngasa akam ak…®riziba. E nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba, e navir ghurim…®n araziba bagha puv agoima, da bar pazav e gami. Ez…® Krais bizir aghuir kaba bar e gan…®ngi. Tuavir kam…®n, a ian akuraght…®, ia arazir kurar kabagh itagh…®va, egh God…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim inigh…®va egh an arazibar amuam.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 2 Pita 3:18\x*Bizir kabanang bagh, ia God…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim inis…® pamten ingar. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n iti. Egh uaghan arazir aghuibar gumazamizir igharazibar amu, egh uaghan God…®n fofozir arazim derav…®ra a inigh.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Galesia 5:22-23\x*Egh uaghan navir ghurim…®n araziba da d…®kab…®n, egh uaghan tugh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba ater, egh uaghan God ifongezir arazibar g…®n mang…®.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Galesia 6:10; 1 Tesalonika 5:15; 1 Jon 4:21\x*Egh uaghan, uan adarazir m…®n, Krais…®n adarazir apangkuvigh men akurvagh. Egh uaghan igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim damu.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Jon 15:2; Taitus 3:14\x*Ia Krais Iesus g…®fo, a en Ekiam. Ia arazir kaba inight…®ma da ian ik…® bar gavgavight…®, ian fofozir kam derav…®ra ingart…®ma, dagher av…®riba otivam.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Hibru 9:14; 1 Jon 1:7; 2:9-11\x*Gumazim o amizim arazir kaba puvat…®gh, a bizir saghuiam…®n tibar ganan kogham, a mati gumazir damazir okav…®r…®zim…®n m…®n ikiam. Guizbang…®ra, God an arazir kurar a fom…®ra amiziba g…®n amada, egha a gamiz…®ma a zue. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir kaba, a da bak…®n…®ghn…®ki.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Pita 3:17; 1 Jon 3:19\x*Nan adarasi, God ian diagha g…®fa, egha ia ginaba, ez…® ia an gumazamizibar ikiam. Kamagh…®n ia zurara an adarazir ik…®v…®ra ik…®va egh bizir kam akakaghs…®, ia bar pamtem ingar. Ia kamagh…®n damu, arazir kuratam…®n ir…®ghan kogh, egh God ateghan kogham.
\v 11 Eght…® a tuavir kam bar ia bagh a kuight…®ma ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven mang…®t…® a ia bagh bar akuegham. Egh dughiar kam…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, a bar Krais Iesus en Ekiam…®n bizim, a en Akurvazir Gumazim.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Filipai 3:1; 1 Pita 5:12; 2 Pita 3:1; 3:17; 1 Jon 2:21; Jut 1:5\x*K…® bizir kaba bagh ia m…®k…®mv…®ra ikiam. Ia guizbang…®ra dagh fogha guiz…®n akam inigha g…®fa, egha an tugha gavgafi.
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 1:13-14 \xt Jon 21:18-19; 2 Korin 5:1; 2 Timoti 4:6; 2 Pita 3:1\x*K…® fo, dughiar bar otevim, k…® nguazir kam…®n itir m…®karzim suevk…®nigham. En Ekiam Krais Iesus kamagh…®n na m…®kemegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n dughiar k…® inivaf…®zir kam…®n aven ikiav…®ra itim, k…® n…®ghn…®zima a dera, k…® ua bizir kaba bagh ia m…®k…®mt…®ma, ia ua dagh n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ikiam.
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bar deragh ia m…®k…®masa. K…® g…®n oveght…®, ia dughiabar zurara bizir k…® ia m…®kemezir kabagh n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ikiam.
\s1 Aposelba uan damazibar God…®n angazangarim…®n garima a Krais…®n iti
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Korin 1:17; 1 Jon 1:1\x*Ez…® dughiar e Krais…®n akar kam…®n ia m…®kemezim, e pura gumazitam…®n eghaghanitam ko n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n ghua ia m…®geir puvat…®. E uan Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n gavgavim ko a ua izamin akam…®n gun ia m…®keme. E faragha guizbang…®ra uan damazibar God…®n angazangarim ko gavgavim…®n garima da Krais Iesus…®n iti, kamagh…®n amiz…® e m…®gei.\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Akar otevir kam a dughiar Iesus…®n m…®karzim igharagha gara otozir bizibav m…®gei. N…® Matyu 17:1-3 ko Mak 9:2-13 ko Luk 9:28-36…®n gan.\f*
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Matyu 3:17\x*\x - \xo 1:17-18 \xt Matyu 17:1-5; Mak 9:2-7; Luk 9:28-35\x*Ez…® God Afeziam ziar ekiam a gan…®ngi, egha angazangarir aghuir kam gamiz…®ma an an oto. Ez…® God uab…® uan Nguibam…®n ikia angazangarir ekiar kam…®n aven ikiava kamagh…®n Iesus m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar nan Otarim, k…® bar a gifonge, egha k…® a bagha bar akonge.‚Äù
\v 18 Ez…® e uari a ko God…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n ikia egha akar kam barazima a God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izaghir…®.
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Onger Akaba 119:105; Jon 5:35\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akabar iti. Ez…® ia uaghan men akabar suiragh gavgavigh, egh deragham. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba mati lam m…®tatem…®n ikia isi mogh…®n, Krais…®n angazangarim ian navir averiabar aven ik…® isiam. Arazir kam mati am…®nim itir m…®kovezim overiam…®n isit…®, m…®tatem mang…®t…® angazangarim otogham.\f + \fr 1:19 \ft M…®zarazim…®n m…®kovezir kam, kar Krais Iesus. N…® Akar Mogomem 22:16…®n gan.\f*
\p 
\v 20-21 \x - \xo 1:20-21 \xt Aposel 1:16; 3:18; Rom 12:6; 2 Timoti 3:16; 1 Pita 1:11\x*Fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akatam, pura gumazitam o amizitam a m…®kemez…® an a m…®geir puvat…®. God…®n Duam uab…® me gaghuavk…®rima me God…®n izezir akam akuri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bizir ekiar kam g…®fogh, God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, me uan n…®ghn…®zibar God…®n Ak…®nafarim osirizir puvat…®.
\c 2
\s1 Ifavarir tisaba Krais…®n adarazir n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa
\r (Jut 4-13)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Matyu 24:11; Aposel 20:30; 1 Timoti 4:1; 2 Timoti 3:1-5; 1 Pita 1:18; Jut 1:4\x*Ez…® fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir ifavarir maba, me Israelian gumazamizibar tong…®n iti. Ez…® kamagh…®ra ifavarir tisaba uaghan ian tong…®n ikiam. Egh me n…®m…®ra ia gifar, God…®n bizitaba ian sure damuam. Egh me mong…®va akar ifavaribar amut…®, da ian tong…®n otivam, kar akar ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gas…®ghas…®ziba. Ekiam ua me ini, eght…® me uamategh ak…®rim ragh, Ekiam gasaragham. Me kamagh…®n damut…®, God zuam…®ra me gas…®ghasigham.
\v 2 Eght…® gumazamizir av…®rim men arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kurabar g…®n mangam. Eght…® bizir kam gumazamizibar amut…® me akar kurabar guizbang…®n tuavir God…®n g…®n zuim…®n m…®k…®mam.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Rom 16:18; 2 Korin 12:17-18; 1 Tesalonika 2:5; 1 Timoti 6:5; Taitus 1:11; 2 Pita 1:16\x*Ifavarir tisan kaba dag…®ar av…®riba baka, kamagh…®n me eghaghanir ifavarir av…®ribar amuva, ian dag…®aba ko biziba iniam. Fom…®ra God me is…® kot dar…®ghasa dughiam at…®gha, ghaze, me bar ikuvigham. Ez…® God akuir puvat…®. A fom…®ra me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n me gas…®ghas…®ghasa me bagha gara iti.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Luk 8:31; Jon 8:44; 1 Jon 3:8; Jut 1:6; Akar Mogomem 20:2-3\x*Ia fo, bar fom…®ra ensel…®n maba arazir kurabagh ami, ez…® God me ataghizir puvat…®. A senbar me ikegha hel…®n me akuniz…®ma me m…®tater bar ekiam…®n aven ti. Me kalabus…®n ikiav…®ra ikia God…®n kotiam…®n dughiam bagha m…®zua iti.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Jenesis 6:1--7:24; Jenesis 8:18; Hibru 11:7; 1 Pita 3:20; 2 Pita 3:6\x*Ez…® gumazamizir bar fom…®ra ikeziba, me God…®n akam barazir puvat…®. Ez…® a me gas…®ghas…®ki. An aperiam gamiz…®ma an otogha bar me kuavareme. Ez…® Noa a gumazir arazir aghuibara gun m…®geir mam, God a ko 7plan gumazamizir igharaziba bar deragha men garima me derav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jenesis 19:24; D…®boboniba 26:10; Jut 1:7\x*Ez…® God Sodom…®n nguibam ko Gomoran nguibam m…®g…®a ghaze, aning uaghan ikuvigham. God aning gaboroz…® aning bar isigha, averenir k…®niba iti. Ez…® g…®n gumazir God…®n akaba batoziba, me bizir Sodom ko Gomoran otozim g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh fogham bizir kam g…®n uaghan me bativam.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jenesis 19:1-16\x*Ez…® God Lot…®n akura, gumazir derav…®ra itim. Egha a, men arazir m…®z…®r…®zibar gara an navim bar a baseme.
\v 8 Gumazir aghuir kam Lot men tong…®n ikia egha men arazir bar kurabar gari. Egha dughiabar zurara men akar kuraba barasi. Ez…® an navim deragha iti. Ez…® a me God…®n Araziba batozir arazim bagha an navim bar ikufi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Onger Akaba 34:17-19; 1 Korin 10:13; Jut 1:6\x*Ekiam amizir biziba, e dagh n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n fo, os…®mt…®zitam gumazamizir God…®n Arazibar g…®n zui taba batogham, God os…®mt…®zir kam uam me da a iniamin tuavim g…®fo. Ez…® God arazir kurabagh amir gumazamizibagh fo, egha men arazir kuraba ikarvaghamin tuavim g…®fo, mamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®va God…®n Kot…®n Ekiam…®n Dughiam otogham.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Jut 1:4-10; 1:16\x*Eght…® gumazamizitaba ivezir kurar bar ekiaba iniam. Kar gumazamizir poroghamiba uari isava akuava amir arazir bar m…®z…®r…®ziba. Egha me God…®n akam m…®g…®a ghaze, a pura bizim.
\p Ez…® gumazamizir kurar kaba ian tong…®n iti, gumazamizir akaba batogha egha uan n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n zuiba. Egha me atiatir puvat…®gha akar kurabar ensel…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n itibav gei.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Jut 1:9\x*Ez…® enselba bar gavgavir ekiam ikia, bar gumazamizir kabagh afira. Egha enselba uari akar kurabar me m…®geir puvat…®, egha Ekiam…®n damazim…®n akam me gasir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Jut 1:10\x*Ez…® ifavarir tisan kaba, me mati as…®zibar m…®n n…®ghn…®ziba puvat…®, egha me uan m…®karzibar ifongiabar arui. Egha me mati as…®zir atiabar m…®n nguazim…®n otifi, eght…® gumaziba men suigh…®va me m…®soght…®ma me ar…®ghiram. Ez…® bizir me fozir puvat…®zim, me akar kurabar a m…®gei. Ez…® arazir kamra mati gumaziba as…®zir atiaba gas…®ghas…®zi mogh…®n God me gas…®ghas…®gham.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Rom 13:13; 1 Korin 11:20-21; Filipai 3:19; Jut 1:12\x*Ez…® me amizir arazir kurabar, gumazamiziba men arazir kaba bagh ua arazir kurabar me ikarvagham. Me ghaze, aruebar dagher ekiaba apir arazim ko d…®par onganiba apir arazim, kar arazir bar aghuim. Egha me ia koma apava, egha ia gamima ia bar m…®ze, egha ian ziabagh as…®ghas…®si. Egha me uan ifavarir arazir me amiba bagha bar akonge.
\v 14 Egha me zurara amizibar gara, arazir kurabar me damuasa n…®ghn…®si. Egha me arazir kurar amiba g…®vasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Me gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir muziariba itibagh ifarima me arazir kurabagh ami. Egha me igharaz darazir bizibar garava, dagh ifongezir arazim bar me giz…®fa. Eght…® God bar me gas…®ghasigham!
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Jut 1:11; Akar Mogomem 2:14\x*\x - \xo 2:15-16 \xt D…®boboniba 22:4-35\x*Me tuavir aghuim ategha, bar onganigha tintinibar zui. Me Beor…®n otarim Balam…®n tuavim…®n g…®n zui. An arazir kuram gamigha, egha uan arazir kurar kam…®n ivezim iniasa.
\v 16 Donkiba m…®geir puvat…®. Ez…® donkin mam gumazim…®n m…®n m…®g…®a Balam…®n arazir kuraba bagha an atari. Ez…® arazir kam…®n, donki God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam gamima, a uan arazir onganir a damuasa n…®ghn…®zim ataki.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Jut 1:12-13\x*Gumazamizir kaba, mati mozir d…®paba dakez…® mogh…®n iti, egha uaghan mati am…®nir ekiam ghuariam givava amadima a tintinibar zuima amoziba puvat…®. God me bagha danganir bar m…®tategha bar p…®ghizim ak…®riz…®ma a iti. Eght…® me mang…®va an ikiam.
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Aposel 2:40; 2 Pita 1:4; 2:20; Jut 1:16\x*Gumazamizir kaba pura tiariba akara egha uan akar onganir kabav g…®a ghaze, erara dera. Me gumazamiziba apezepera me gamima, me naviba d…®kavava arazir poroghamiba uari isava akuiba, ko inivaf…®zim…®n arazir kurar igharazibar amuasa n…®ghn…®si. Ez…® arazir kam…®n, me gumazamizir dat…®r…®gh…®ra navibagh iragha arazir kuraba ataghiziba, me me gamima, me gumazamizir kurar kabar g…®n zui.
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Jon 8:34; Rom 6:16; 1 Pita 2:16\x*Gumazamizir kurar kaba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n ia en g…®n mang…®va, egh ia f…®righ…®regh uan n…®ghn…®zibar ifongezir bizibar amuam.‚Äù Men arazir kuraba me gas…®ghas…®zima, me uari pura ingangarir gumazamiziba. E fo, gumazamiziba bizitam me ik…®raright…®, me bizir kam…®n pura ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®n ikiam.
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Matyu 12:45; Luk 11:26; Hibru 6:4; 2 Pita 1:2-4\x*Guizbang…®ra, me en Ekiam Krais Iesus da fofozim inis, a en Akurvazir Gumazim. Ez…® fofozir kam men akuraz…® me arazir m…®z…®r…®zir nguazim…®n itiba bar adagh ita. Egh kamagh…®n me ua arazir kurabar amut…®, da ua me ik…®rar…®gh egh bar me gafiragham. Eght…® men ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®n bar mogh…®ra bar ikuvigh fom…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim gafiragham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Luk 12:47-48; Jon 9:41\x*Kamagh…®n me arazir aghuim…®n tuavim g…®fozir puvat…®gha, deraghai. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me tuavir kam g…®fo, egha God…®n akaba ini, egha uam ak…®rim ragha God gasara. Ez…® bizir kam bagh me bar ikuvigham.
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 26:11\x*Ez…® bizir men otozir kam, guiz…®n akar otevir mam…®n aven kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAfiam migha egha ghua ua uan mimiziba api.‚Äù Ez…® uaghan akar otevir igharazir mam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDam d…®pam guregha g…®vagha ua ghua beghneazim g…®poghposi.‚Äù Aning…®n arazim v…®rara bar kufi.
\c 3
\s1 Bar guizbang…®ra Ekiam ua izam
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt 2 Pita 1:13\x*Nan roroaba, kar nan namba 2…®n ak…®nafarim k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia bagha an osiri. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ak…®nafarir k…® osirizir kamning, ian n…®ghn…®ziba uam a da feght…®, ia ua bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®ghv…®ra ikiam, egh ian n…®ghn…®ziba bar derav…®ra ikiam.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Jut 1:17\x*Ia ua God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba fom…®ra m…®kemezir akabagh n…®ghn…®ghasa k…® ifonge. Egh ia uaghan Ekiam…®n akabagh n…®ghn…®gh, a en Akurvazir Gumazim. Ia uan aposelba da akar kam inis.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Timoti 4:1; 2 Timoti 3:1; 2 Pita 2:10; Jut 1:18\x*Ia faragh bizir ekiar kam g…®fogh, Ekiam ua izamin dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba uan navir ghurim…®n arazibar g…®n mang…®va d…®bovir akar kurabar ia m…®k…®mam.
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Aisaia 5:19; Jeremaia 17:15; Esekiel 12:22; 12:27; Matyu 24:48; Luk 12:45\x*Me kamagh…®n ia d…®povam, ‚ÄúIesus ghaze, a ti ua izam, o? Egha a managh iti? A izan kogham. En ovavir ovengeziba ua d…®kavan kogham. Ez…® biziba fom…®ra nguazim otozir dughiam…®n iti mogh…®n ikia iza dat…®r…®k…®n.‚Äù
